---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Protocols
permalink: /protocols/
---

<p>Writing about the open protocols that make an independent web possible — Gemini, ActivityPub, RSS, Gopher, and the infrastructure beneath them.</p>

{% if collections.protocols.length %}
  {% set grouped = collections.protocols | groupByYear %}
  {% for group in grouped %}
    <h2>{{ group.year }}</h2>
    <ul class="archive-list">
    {% for post in group.posts %}
      <li>
        <span class="archive-date">{{ post.date | dateToFormat("MMM d") }}</span>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% endfor %}
{% else %}
  <p>First protocol piece coming soon.</p>
{% endif %}
